  ('GG4', 'gg4', 'hybrid', 'Also known as Original Glue — a famously sticky, heavy-hitting hybrid of Chem''s Sister, Sour Dubb, and Chocolate Diesel. Delivers deep couch-lock relaxation with a pungent diesel-chocolate funk.', array['Relaxed','Sleepy','Euphoric','Happy'], array['Earthy','Diesel','Pungent'], array['Caryophyllene','Myrcene','Limonene'], array['Chem''s Sister','Sour Dubb','Chocolate Diesel'], 20, 28),
